<br>
Normally I  mostly just dont answer to any requests but sow and bind.  So I just pretend most of the people arent there. <br>
Yes I know this is rude, but theres way to many of them.<br>
<br>
Anyway this one hobbit was sending tells, and standing between me and my mule, and just being irritating, and getting more and more mad at me as i ignored him i guess, cause a few minutes later my Mule gets a tell...<br>
<br>
&quot;That Iisbliss is such a bitch, dont try to get anything from her, I think she must be afk&quot;<br>
<br>
well my Mule was sympathetic, and replied to him &quot;Yeah these high levels think they can just do what they want and ignore people, I hate them.  Can you spare some PP?&quot;<br>
<br>
he answered &quot;No I've been asking for PP here for hours now and no one has given me any.&quot;<br>
<br>
oh well = )<br>
